Rakuen has no direct route connection to the Great Northern Forest. The forest is relevant primarily as a factor in Midgaard's supply health: Lantern Road disruptions affect Midgaard's northern grain and timber inputs, cascading into Midgaard's capacity to supply Rakuen through the Eccentric Woodland corridor. During the Ash Winters, the same Cinderteeth volcanic activity that disrupted Lantern Road traffic also disrupted the Eccentric Woodland approaches — Rakuen experienced both supply chains degrading simultaneously, without either Midgaard or Kowloon able to prioritize Rakuen's needs over their own.

flags MAFDET
